---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Welcome from "../components/Welcome.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import { CldImage } from "astro-cloudinary";
---

<Layout>
  <Welcome />
  <!-- Footer-like contact section at bottom -->

  <div class="pt-16 pb-8 px-4 md:px-16">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Main Content -->
      <div
        class="mb-16 fade-in font-sans text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed max-w-prose"
      >
        <p class="mb-4">
          Brilliant engineering shouldn't stop at a blueprint. Thinkin'Rocks
          bridges the gap between concept and reality by providing managed
          access to the cutting-edge
          <a
            href="/hardware"
            class="text-purple-600 hover:text-purple-800 transition-colors"
            >hardware</a
          >—from neurowearables and FPGAs to humanoid robots—that usually sit
          behind corporate firewalls.
        </p>

        <p class="mb-4">
          The tools are only as powerful as the hands wielding them. We amplify
          raw compute with human expertise, anchoring our facility within a
          network of deep-tech leaders like Varjo, Alif Semiconductor, and
          Doublepoint. Explore the <a
            href="/about"
            class="text-purple-600 hover:text-purple-800 transition-colors"
            >partners and team</a
          > driving this ecosystem.
        </p>

        <p class="mb-4">
          Ideas creates noise; we capture the signal. Our facility is a living
          record of continuous testing, breaking, and shipping. To see the raw
          engineering process and what is currently on our workbenches, read the <a
            href="/log"
            class="text-purple-600 hover:text-purple-800 transition-colors"
            >logs</a
          >.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Contact Section -->
      <div class="fade-in">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 mb-6">
          <div class="bg-purple-600 h-fit translate-0.5">
            <a
              href="https://tally.so/r/mBrVg7"
              class="bg-purple-50 text-purple-600 inline-flex px-6 py-3 -translate-0.5 items-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap font-mono hover:bg-purple-100 transition-colors"
              data-umami-event="join-us-click"
            >
              Join Us
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-600 h-fit translate-0.5">
            <a
              href="mailto:milana@thinkinrocks.com"
              class="bg-gray-50 text-gray-600 inline-flex px-6 py-3 -translate-0.5 items-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap font-mono hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors"
              data-umami-event="contact-us-click"
            >
              Contact Us
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
